<p>Experiencing The Exploratorium as a visitor is like surfing the web without ever contributing content. Frank Oppenheimer&#8217;s vision extended to more than just an experience for visitor&#8217;s.  The experience starts with the creator&#8217;s of the learning displays. Why don&#8217;t you make a display there yourself? The institution is  pretty open, or at least it used to be.</p>

